	{"heading":"Stardate 2401.0 (Economic Phase 1)",
	"commentary":"<p>Regardless, this is probably one of the most explosive openings in <i>any</i> Space Empires 4X playthrough. The Replicators have managed to uncover <i>15</i> hexes (including 5 planets). Their economics are very simple; only extra hulls (-8 each) until the fourth economic phase.</p><p>Granted, our Ancient Race contributed sharply to our own explosive opening, since several hexes were pre-revealed and <span class=\"bindTxt\">(as appropriate)</span> pre-claimed before the first turns even took place. We buy Exploration 1 (-15). We then buy 2 Colony Ships (-16), 2 Pipelines (-6), and an extra Ship Yard (-6) at our homeworld.</p>",
